  "chapter": {
    "number": 5,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "The Day of the Lord"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 1,
        "content": [
          "Now about the times and seasons, brothers, we do not need to write to you."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 2,
        "content": [
          "For you are fully aware that the Day of the Lord will come like a thief in the night."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 3,
        "content": [
          "While people are saying, “Peace and security,” destruction will come upon them suddenly, like labor pains on a pregnant woman, and they will not escape."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 4,
        "content": [
          "But you, brothers, are not in the darkness so that this day should overtake you like a thief."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 5,
        "content": [
          "For you are all sons of the light and sons of the day; we do not belong to the night or to the darkness."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 6,
        "content": [
          "So then, let us not sleep as the others do, but let us remain awake and sober."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 7,
        "content": [
          "For those who sleep, sleep at night; and those who get drunk, get drunk at night."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 8,
        "content": [
          "But since we belong to the day, let us be sober, putting on the breastplate of faith and love, and the helmet of our hope of salvation."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 9,
        "content": [
          "For God has not appointed us to suffer wrath, but to obtain salvation through our Lord Jesus Christ."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 10,
        "content": [
          "He died for us so that, whether we are awake or asleep, we may live together with Him."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 11,
        "content": [
          "Therefore encourage and build one another up, just as you are already doing."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "Christian Living"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 12,
        "content": [
          "But we ask you, brothers, to acknowledge those who work diligently among you, who preside over you in the Lord and give you instruction."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 13,
        "content": [
          "In love, hold them in highest regard because of their work. Live in peace with one another."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 14,
        "content": [
          "And we urge you, brothers, to admonish the unruly, encourage the fainthearted, help the weak, and be patient with everyone."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 15,
        "content": [
          "Make sure that no one repays evil for evil. Always pursue what is good for one another and for all people."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 16,
        "content": [
          "Rejoice at all times."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 17,
        "content": [
          "Pray without ceasing."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 18,
        "content": [
          "Give thanks in every circumstance, for this is God’s will for you in Christ Jesus."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 19,
        "content": [
          "Do not extinguish the Spirit."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 20,
        "content": [
          "Do not treat prophecies with contempt,"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 21,
        "content": [
          "but test all things. Hold fast to what is good."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 22,
        "content": [
          "Abstain from every form of evil."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "Final Blessings and Instructions"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 23,
        "content": [
          "Now may the God of peace Himself sanctify you completely, and may your entire spirit, soul, and body be kept blameless",
          {
            "noteId": 611
          },
          "at the coming of our Lord Jesus Christ."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 24,
        "content": [
          "The One who calls you is faithful, and He will do it."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 25,
        "content": [
          "Brothers, pray for us as well."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 26,
        "content": [
          "Greet all the brothers with a holy kiss."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 27,
        "content": [
          "I charge you before the Lord to have this letter read to all the brothers."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 28,
        "content": [
          "The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you.",
          {
            "noteId": 612
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
